* ScrollManager --- JavaScript/Coffescript html DOM layout handler for interactive scroll based sites or campaigns.

** Usage

I need to write something here but untill then checkout [[https://github.com/alexaivars/ScrollManager/blob/master/public_html/index.html][index.html]] 

** Bugs?

There is a test suite but since these are some of my first tests written in and for
coffeescript and jasmin they need more work. 

** Links

- Project at GitHub: [[http://github.com/alexaivars/ScrollManager][http://github.com/alexaivars/ScrollManager]]

